<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />What advantage is there in my death, if I go down to the grave? Will the dust praise you? Will it declare your trustworthiness?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />Hear, Yahweh, and have mercy on me! Yahweh, be my helper.</para>
